<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Efficiency Gain and Lower Transaction Costs</h2>



<p>Layer-2 Rollups on Polygon significantly enhance efficiency by aggregating multiple transactions into a single batch, thereby reducing congestion on the Ethereum network and lowering gas fees. </p>



<p>By utilizing Rollups, transactions can be processed off-chain and then settled on the Ethereum mainnet, resulting in substantial cost savings for users.</p>



<p>Additionally, the implementation of Rollups ensures faster transaction finality and improved scalability, addressing the challenges associated with high gas costs and network congestion.</p>



