<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can Users Seamlessly Switch Between the Ethereum Mainnet and Polygon Layer-2 Solutions?</h3>



<p>Yes, users can seamlessly switch between the Ethereum mainnet and Polygon Layer-2 solutions. This interoperability is a key feature, providing flexibility and cost-efficiency for transactions and dapp usage.</p>



